Barcelona Soccer Player Messi’s Home Shot 6 Times in Argentina, C5N Says

-- B y   R o d r i g o   O r i h u e l a
-- 
2011-04-11T13:22:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/barcelona-soccer-player-messi-s-home-shot-6-times-in-argentina-c5n-says.html
A house owned by Argentine soccer
player  Lionel Messi , twice named the sport’s best player by its
governing body, was shot at six times over the weekend, Buenos
Aires-based television channel C5N reported.  The Barcelona soccer team striker’s home in Rosario,
 Argentina , was hit four times by bullets, C5N said. No one was
hurt in the attack, the network reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rodrigo Orihuela in Buenos Aires at 
 rorihuela@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bill Faries at 
 wfaries@bloomberg.net  